actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution directing the Senate Legal Counsel to represent the Acting Public Printer in the Honorable Alcee L. Hastings, United States District Judge v. The United States Senate, et al. (D.D.C.).

summary.text: Directs the Senate Legal Counsel to represent Joseph E. Jenifer, the Acting Public Printer of the United States, in the case of The Honorable Alcee L. Hastings, United States District Judge v. The United States Senate, et al.

titles.title: A resolution directing the Senate Legal Counsel to represent the Acting Public Printer in the Honorable Alcee L. Hastings, United States District Judge v. The United States Senate, et al. (D.D.C.).
